Clisonix has developed advanced EEG analysis systems that make brain-computer

42
00:02:29,521 --> 00:02:34,923
interfaces more accessible and reliable. Our ALBA system provides real-time

43
00:02:34,923 --> 00:02:40,325
EEG signal processing with high accuracy. ALBI handles peripheral data

44
00:02:40,325 --> 00:02:45,727
integration for comprehensive neural monitoring. And JONA coordinates these systems

45
00:02:45,727 --> 00:02:51,129
for seamless industrial-grade performance. Together with the Curiosity Ocean AI,

46
00:02:51,129 --> 00:02:56,531
we're making brain technology more intuitive and powerful than ever

47
00:02:56,531 --> 00:03:01,933
before.

50
00:02:57,072 --> 00:03:01,766
The future of brain-computer interfaces is incredibly promising. Advances in

51
00:03:01,766 --> 00:03:06,461
electrode technology will make BCIs less invasive and more comfortable.

52
00:03:06,461 --> 00:03:11,156
Machine learning improvements will enable faster, more accurate signal interpretation.

53
00:03:11,156 --> 00:03:15,851
And miniaturization will lead to wearable BCIs that integrate seamlessly

54
00:03:15,851 --> 00:03:20,546
into daily life. We're moving toward a world where the

55
00:03:20,546 --> 00:03:25,241
boundary between mind and machine becomes increasingly fluid, opening new

56
00:03:25,241 --> 00:03:29,936
possibilities for human potential.

59
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:31,876
Brain-Computer Interfaces represent a paradigm shift in how we interact

60
00:03:31,876 --> 00:03:36,632
with technology. From helping patients regain lost abilities to enhancing

61
00:03:36,632 --> 00:03:41,388
human cognition, BCIs are not just science fiction鍟hey're becoming reality.

62
00:03:41,388 --> 00:03:46,144
At Clisonix, we're proud to be part of this revolution,

63
00:03:46,144 --> 00:03:50,900
building the tools that will shape the future of neural

64
00:03:50,900 --> 00:03:55,656
technology. Thank you for watching. To learn more, visit clisonix.com.
